ng> </strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>gastados</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>de</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>EDTA</strong></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"39\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.1in; margin-right: 0.04in; text-indent: -0.04in; margin-top: 0.04in; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>factor </strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>(real)</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>obtenido</strong></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"border-style: none solid solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"45\">\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.18in; margin-right: 0.16in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>T1</strong></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-style: none solid solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"40\">\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.12in; margin-right: 0.1in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>T2</strong></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-style: none solid solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"40\">\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.12in; margin-right: 0.1in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>T3</strong></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-style: none solid solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"22\">\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0in; margin-right: -0.03in; margin-top: 0.01in; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><strong>promedio</strong></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n<tbody>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"67\" height=\"8\">\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.2in; margin-right: 0.19in; margin-top: 0in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">BCO</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"120\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"45\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"40\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"40\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"22\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"39\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n<tbody>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"67\" height=\"7\">\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.21in; margin-right: 0.19in; margin-top: 0.01in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">CaCO3</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"120\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"45\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"40\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"40\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"22\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0in;\" width=\"39\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"western\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"margin-top: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">Tomar 10ml de la disolución estándar trazable de CaCO3 y aforara 50 ml con agua destilada, agregar una pizca del indicador negro de Eriocromo T, y titular con la disolución 0.01 M, de un vire rojo a azul. Titular por triplicado la disolución EDTA y calcular un factor promedio.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'null', NULL, NULL, '2023-06-06 00:50:34', NULL);
